    "description": {
      "value": "<p>As an action, you can reach into your @UUID[Compendium.materia-dnd.class-and-subclass-features.Item.l9H7gLFhbj9XBfEu]{Alchemist's Satchel} and pull out a crystalline shard and hurl it at a creature, object, or surface within 30 feet of you. The shard shatters on impact with a blast of concussive energy. Each creature of huge size or smaller within 10 feet of the point of impact must succeed on a Constitution saving throw or be knocked prone and pushed 10 feet away from that point if they are Huge or Large; pushed 15 feet away if they are Medium or smaller.</p>",
